), supporting this hypothesis and indicating that deceptive environmental claims erode consumer trust, which is crucial for the long-term success of fintech firms [2]. Hypothesis H3 asserts that industry professionals perceive greenwashing as a threat to the credibility of the fintech industry. The independent t-test result was significant (t = 2.46, 


