), confirming this hypothesis and corroborating studies that professionals within the fintech sector recognize the damage greenwashing can inflict on the industry's reputation [20], [21]. The fourth hypothesis (H4) posits that an effective regulatory framework can reduce greenwashing in fintech. The Chi-square test result was significant (



